data.description: This beautiful spacious home is ready for new owners! From the moment you enter you will notice the elevated ceilings, crown molding and bright open floor plan.  An expansive kitchen with stainless appliances, granite counters, breakfast bar, island, tiled back splash, and plenty of cabinets will delight any chef. Living room, family room, kitchen, dining, 1/2 bath & laundry are situated downstairs. Upstairs is a large bonus/media room along with 4 bedrooms & family bathroom. The very spacious owners suite boasts of a sitting area, walk in closet, double sinks, beautiful walk-in shower and a garden tub to relax in at the end of the day.  Relax in the large screened porch. Home is sited on a corner lot with lovely landscaping and plenty of room for a pool! New roof and newer A/C. Hurry!!!!
